overview: Red Ryder and his comical sidekick take on a new batch of bad-guys in this western, the 16th in the Red Ryder series. This time the heroic duo try to save a female rancher from a greedy financier who wants her land so he can exploit the enormous oil fields lying under it.
tagline: BLAZING OIL...ROARING GUNS! in a thrill-packed story of daring adventure!
title: Conquest of Cheyenne
